{
  "rationale": "To ensure efficient arena coverage while maintaining safety, the supervisor uses systematic wall-following when obstacles are detected and resumes systematic movement when clear. Helper states (e.g., wall_follow_left) manage obstacle-adjacent behaviors, preventing oscillations and promoting full coverage. All uncontrollable events are handled in every state to ensure responsiveness.",
  "new_states": [
