  "coverage_strategy": [
    "In clear state, use systematic moves (move_forward, full_rotate, random_walk) to cover open areas.",
    "On detecting an obstacle, switch to the corresponding obstacle state to react safely.",
    "Initiate wall-following (left or right) upon clearing a front obstacle to systematically sweep boundaries.",
    "Return to clear state when path is open to resume systematic coverage.",
    "Wall-following states prevent oscillation and allow for efficient perimeter tracing.",
    "Transitions between wall-following and clear states ensure both boundary and open-area coverage."
